### 🧪 Chess Trainer API Interactive Tests

# Set base URL
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 📋 Test 1: Get All Games
GET {{baseUrl}}/chess/games
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 🔍 Test 2: Search Games (cmess user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chess/games?search=cmess&page=1&page_size=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 📊 Test 3: Get Sources Dropdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/chess/games/sources
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 🎯 Test 4: Search by Source
GET {{baseUrl}}/chess/games?source=elite&page=1&page_size=5
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 🔍 Test 5: Combined Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/chess/games?search=cmess&source=elite&page=1&page_size=3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 📈 Test 6: Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###